) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (

    INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]

        INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
        INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN [Couriers] AS [c] ON [o].[CourierId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [c].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[CreatedDate] DESC, [o].[Id], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN [Couriers] AS [c] ON [o].[CourierId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [c].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[CreatedDate] DESC, [o].[Id], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [c].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[CreatedDate] DESC, [o].[Id], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[CourierId], [o].[CreatedDate], [o].[CustomerId], [o].[DeliveredAt], [o].[DeliveryAddress], [o].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [o].[Notes], [o].[PaymentMethod], [o].[Status], [o].[TotalPrice], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[MenuItemId], [t].[OrderId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id0], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Description], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[Id1], [t].[CreatedDate1], [t].[Name0], [t].[RestaurantId], [t].[Id2], [t].[Address], [t].[CreatedDate2], [t].[DeliveryCost], [t].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t].[Image0], [t].[Name1], [t].[Phone], [t].[RestaurantCategoryId], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[IsAvailable], [c].[UserId], [c].[VehicleType], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FullName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [c0].[Address], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[UserId], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[FullName], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN [Couriers] AS [c] ON [o].[CourierId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [c].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[CreatedDate] DESC, [o].[Id], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN [Couriers] AS [c] ON [o].[CourierId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [c].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [o].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a0] ON [c0].[UserId] = [a0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[CreatedDate], [o0].[MenuItemId], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [m0].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name1], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]

    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [o0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [o].[CreatedDate] DESC, [o].[Id], [c].[Id], [a].[Id], [c0].[Id], [a0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1]

INNER JOIN [RestaurantCategories] AS [r0] ON [r].[RestaurantCategoryId] = [r0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [RestaurantReviews] AS [r1] ON [r].[Id] = [r1].[RestaurantId]
ORDER BY [r].[Id], [r0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]

    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CustomerId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[MenuItemId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[MenuItemId0], [t0].[Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate00], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Name0], [t0].[CreatedDate2], [t0].[Name1], [t0].[RestaurantId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedDate3], [t0].[DeliveryCost], [t0].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t0].[Image0], [t0].[Name2], [t0].[Phone], [t0].[RestaurantCategoryId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CustomerId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[MenuItemId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[MenuItemId0], [t0].[Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate00], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Name0], [t0].[CreatedDate2], [t0].[Name1], [t0].[RestaurantId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedDate3], [t0].[DeliveryCost], [t0].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t0].[Image0], [t0].[Name2], [t0].[Phone], [t0].[RestaurantCategoryId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CustomerId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[MenuItemId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[MenuItemId0], [t0].[Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate00], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Name0], [t0].[CreatedDate2], [t0].[Name1], [t0].[RestaurantId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedDate3], [t0].[DeliveryCost], [t0].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t0].[Image0], [t0].[Name2], [t0].[Phone], [t0].[RestaurantCategoryId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CustomerId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[MenuItemId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[MenuItemId0], [t0].[Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate00], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Name0], [t0].[CreatedDate2], [t0].[Name1], [t0].[RestaurantId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedDate3], [t0].[DeliveryCost], [t0].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t0].[Image0], [t0].[Name2], [t0].[Phone], [t0].[RestaurantCategoryId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]

    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]

    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]

        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]

    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CustomerId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CartId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[MenuItemId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Image], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3], [t0].[CreatedDate1], [t0].[DiscountId], [t0].[MenuItemId0], [t0].[Id00], [t0].[CreatedDate00], [t0].[DiscountPercentage], [t0].[EndDate], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[Name0], [t0].[CreatedDate2], [t0].[Name1], [t0].[RestaurantId], [t0].[Address], [t0].[CreatedDate3], [t0].[DeliveryCost], [t0].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [t0].[Image0], [t0].[Name2], [t0].[Phone], [t0].[RestaurantCategoryId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CustomerId]
    FROM [Carts] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CustomerId] = @__customerId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CartId], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[MenuItemId], [c0].[Quantity], [m].[Id] AS [Id0], [m].[CategoryId], [m].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [m].[Description], [m].[Image], [m].[Name], [m].[Price], [m0].[Id] AS [Id1], [r].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[Id] AS [Id3], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [t1].[DiscountId], [t1].[MenuItemId] AS [MenuItemId0], [t1].[Id0] AS [Id00], [t1].[CreatedDate0] AS [CreatedDate00], [t1].[DiscountPercentage], [t1].[EndDate], [t1].[IsActive], [t1].[Name] AS [Name0], [m0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate2], [m0].[Name] AS [Name1], [m0].[RestaurantId], [r].[Address], [r].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate3], [r].[DeliveryCost], [r].[EstimatedDeliveryTime], [r].[Image] AS [Image0], [r].[Name] AS [Name2], [r].[Phone], [r].[RestaurantCategoryId]
    FROM [CartItems] AS [c0]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItems] AS [m] ON [c0].[MenuItemId] = [m].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [MenuItemCategories] AS [m0] ON [m].[CategoryId] = [m0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Restaurants] AS [r] ON [m0].[RestaurantId] = [r].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [m1].[Id], [m1].[CreatedDate], [m1].[DiscountId], [m1].[MenuItemId], [d].[Id] AS [Id0], [d].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [d].[DiscountPercentage], [d].[EndDate], [d].[IsActive], [d].[Name]
        FROM [MenuItemDiscounts] AS [m1]
        INNER JOIN [Discounts] AS [d] ON [m1].[DiscountId] = [d].[Id]
    ) AS [t1] ON [m].[Id] = [t1].[MenuItemId]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[Id3]
